      "date": "2012-03-09 23:07:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI had a quick look through this. Do you have any performance numbers for Nehalem+ and also older CPUs?\n\nWhat algorithm is chosen by default now?\n\nWhy no CRC32c for userspace?",
