      "date": "2012-03-20 06:39:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nLook at LU-1201, we discuss this question with Andreas, already. Crc32c for user level, - I can add, if it`s needed. \nFirst patch have issue with build for 2.6.18 kernel, because there is no hash_desc. Minor change for linux-crypto.c resolve the issue\n#ifndef HAVE_STRUCT_HASH_DESC\nstruct hash_desc {\n        struct crypto_hash *tfm;\n        u32 flags;\n};\n#endif",
