      "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\npatch reverted due ofa rh5 build fail, new request at http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,30985\nTwo lines changed linux-crypto.c crypto_tfm_alg_name(crypto_hash_tfm(desc->tfm) to \n(crypto_hash_tfm(desc->tfm))->__crt_alg->cra_name\nand the next line above. Root cause of build fail is return type of sruct ncrypto_tfm* crypto_hash_tfm() wich was added by ofa. Struct ncrypto_tfm is the same like crypto_tfm, but there is new union member and mirrored crypto_alg struct.",
